map_npcs.name: Boostgem Researcher
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Have you found any more crystals on your journey?
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
We've been researching these gems that occur naturally in the surrounding areas.
They seem to boost the strength of Oochamon, maybe give one of these a try?

map_npcs.name: Cave Guard
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Can't let you through without the boss's permission.

map_npcs.name: Head Engineer
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Any luck with the Lavaboard Prototype?
They took off through that there cave just to the East.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Oh, you must be the new guy, yeah? 
Did the Head Researcher send you my way?
Ya see, we have a bit of a problem. 
Someone's run off with our Lavaboard Prototype.
They took of sprinting through the cave to the East, if you can retrieve it that'd be a huge help!
{objective:Retrieve the stolen Lavaboard Prototype}

map_npcs.name: Raider Zara
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Oi, this is my stash! Get outta here!

map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Hmmm, I suppose you'll suffice.
I'm sure we'll be seeing eachother soon.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
My, my, you must be {player}.
I've heard of your work so far, but I'd like to propose a small test of your skills.

map_npcs.name: Crew Denny
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: I think I'm gonna take some time to go cool off...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
You'd think working so close to lava flows would be way too hot...
And it is!

map_npcs.name: Crew Dustin
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Oh, my bad, there was a pebble in my boot!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Watch where you're goin I'm workin' here!

map_npcs.name: Researcher Charles
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Hmm, the oochamon in this area seem to be mostly Flame-type.
But I guess that makes sense considering where we are...
...
Oh, hey, I just caught these, help me test their performance!

map_npcs.name: Stranded Researcher
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Oh me? Don't worry too much, I stocked up on like 200 Cooling Balms.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Ha, ha, funny prank guys, leave me out here in the middle of the lava.
Good thing I have so many Cooling Balms.
You look like you could use some yourself!

map_npcs.name: Cave Guard
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Stay safe, we have a perfect safety record and I hope you'll maintain that.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Ah, got the boss's permission?
Good, it's not safe on the other side of this cave.

map_npcs.name: Distracted Researcher
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Ok, I guess I can give you a *little* spoiler for upcoming content.
There will be more content.
That's the spoiler.
...
Oh also the transition to this cave entrance doesn't even exist yet, so good luck getting through.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Oh, maybe try coming back here next patch.
**That's it for this phase of the playtest, don't forget to leave feedback!**

map_npcs.name: Busy Crew
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Looks like it could be a while before this tunnel's safe to enter.

map_npcs.name: Crew Jim
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Fine, fine, I'll get back to work in another five minutes...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Me? I'm on my break.
And I'm definitely not slacking off.

map_npcs.name: Bored Crew
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
I'm so bored, there's nothing to do right now...
Here, take these, I don't have any use for them...

map_npcs.name: Head Engineer
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Great, you'll do just fine on our next request! Here's your completed Lavaboard!
Now, as for our next request...
There's a rather rare material further North of here.
If you hop on your Lavaboard and ride to the West, you'll get where you need to go.
{objective:Ride the Lava River West}
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Ah, perfect, you're back!
If you'll pass me the Lavaboard Prototype...
Hmm... I'll hand this off to another Engineer to tune it.
In the meantime, I'd like to test your strength!
Get ready for another battle!

map_npcs.name: Head Engineer
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
The settlement's a bit of a work in progress.
But we're still hard at work!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Having any luck out there? You can return here any time!

map_shops.greeting_dialogue: Welcome to my store. Buy whatever you need below!
